	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />A second consecutive read is kept by capacitance, a write then a read is kept actively (but not by a keeper, and the data isn't used).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


